tId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"We are developing this theme in the next couple of weeks. ","parentId":"2d489ed3-febd-4f82-90a7-5b135df0dfd3","previousState":null},{"id":"2d489ed3-febd-4f82-90a7-5b135df0dfd3","createdAt":"2023-06-11T20:05:04.061Z","value":0,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"I will be in touch with Marketing during the next couple of weeks next to our process pursuing to validate our ICP.","parentId":"bd0324fd-99c3-4431-a255-589e2446a85d","previousState":null},{"id":"bd0324fd-99c3-4431-a255-589e2446a85d","createdAt":"2023-05-15T13:29:52.469Z","value":10,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"I will review this KR in the current week.","parentId":"9b3dd70a-80aa-464d-a794-739b3f1eca90","previousState":null},{"id":"9b3dd70a-80aa-464d-a794-739b3f1eca90","createdAt":"2023-05-08T11:15:40.321Z","value":10,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"bceef43d-efe0-4216-bf91-9edcfba91f6b","comment":"Mantido","parentId":"f02c7304-aa94-4653-9ca4-ab0142d078ce","previousState":null},{"id":"f02c7304-aa94-4653-9ca4-ab0142d078ce","createdAt":"2023-04-28T17:48:57.242Z","value":10,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"bceef43d-efe0-4216-bf91-9edcfba91f6b","comment":"Caminhando um pouco aqui com dois pontos que refletimos nas últimas duas semanas como principais diferenciais:\n- Guiar o líder para ação\n- Bem estar\n\nE caminhando para trazer AI também. Acho que está mais claro para nós, founders e agora precisamos refletir mais no produto","parentId":"5246f121-b958-4b55-879b-98cd0e86379e","previousState":null},{"id":"5246f121-b958-4b55-879b-98cd0e86379e","createdAt":"2023-04-03T19:44:34.624Z","value":0,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"I must develop a test to verify our hypothesis of bud being the leader's assistant.\n- Market side: It seems there are no competitors with this approach. But we still need to validate if this is a profitable approach for sales. \n- User side: We have evidence that users need clarification of their objectives and KRs and a summary of what happened. We can count those as the product guiding and facilitating how users create and consume strategic information. \n- Funding side: According to Kia and Maurício, the assistance approach is a valuable differential from the investors' perspective. ","parentId":"f23af7cf-6e0e-492d-8339-1cea8e3b9490","previousState":null},{"id":"f23af7cf-6e0e-492d-8339-1cea8e3b9490","createdAt":"2023-03-19T17:10:05.774Z","value":0,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"I will develop a plan during this week to check if clarification of the KRs qualify as a important differential.","parentId":"a89aa32c-db4b-4101-a152-7f21545829ec","previousState":null},{"id":"a89aa32c-db4b-4101-a152-7f21545829ec","createdAt":"2023-03-11T21:20:53.467Z","value":0,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"This week we made some progress in this KR with the discovery process on the new feature about planning clarification and tests from the leader's checklist. ","parentId":"56b505bf-5103-44c7-b0d6-451f85b3ce21","previousState":null},{"id":"56b505bf-5103-44c7-b0d6-451f85b3ce21","createdAt":"2023-02-23T16:54:39.037Z","value":0,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"To make progress in this KR, we first need the concept feature. \n\nOur current hypothesis is that guidance plays a major competitive advantage in the leader's journey through strategy execution. More than giving the tool for strategy execution, we guide our users to evolve their strategy execution routines and practices. ","parentId":"334b1f83-48a8-4b6c-b4c1-291ef117ba17","previousState":null},{"id":"334b1f83-48a8-4b6c-b4c1-291ef117ba17","createdAt":"2023-02-07T22:08:50.194Z","value":0,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"This value is on hold since we are in the design phase of this issue. ","parentId":"b06bf26a-0a92-478c-855b-856fd822cd11","previousState":null},{"id":"b06bf26a-0a92-478c-855b-856fd822cd11","createdAt":"2023-01-30T18:17:13.781Z","value":0,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"Atualmente avançamos com esse tema em produto. Primeiro criando uma leader journey para entender onde podemos apoiar o líder em sua trajetória em strategy execution.\n","parentId":"a52efb13-7e88-4640-8b3a-992ecad3f576","previousState":null},{"id":"a52efb13-7e88-4640-8b3a-992ecad3f576","createdAt":"2023-01-20T14:40:40.253Z","value":0,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"3b897581-d760-46c1-ad52-059d59276bf2","userId":"bceef43d-efe0-4216-bf91-9edcfba91f6b","comment":"ainda não priorizado","parentId":null,"previousState":null}],"objective":{"id":"4f352889-3a4b-4e4b-8fdd-de6371e86e1c","createdAt":"2023-01-13T14:19:59.669Z","title":"Create long-term relevance in our customers","description":null,"updatedAt":"2023-01-13T16:24:12.750Z","cycleId":"4f01f61e-1616-40fa-8363-a930a2db2351","ownerId":"5aec0149-5535-42fb-b3d3-c20a5bda80c8","teamId":"f6790108-2b16-4077-bed0-103fc38175dd","mode":"PUBLISHED","cycle":{"id":"4f01f61e-1616-40fa-8363-a930a2db2351","createdAt":"2023-01-12T18:32:30.038Z","period":"2023","cadence":"YEARLY","active":true,"dateStart":"2023-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","dateEnd":"2023-12-31T00:00:00.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-01-12T18:32:30.038Z","teamId":"f6790108-2b