 but mainly increase Stickiness.","parentId":"8aaac14e-4cf4-4279-a59d-d90eb5b86ea5","previousState":null},{"id":"8aaac14e-4cf4-4279-a59d-d90eb5b86ea5","createdAt":"2023-05-15T13:22:05.762Z","value":67.72,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"6f488fb4-a4cf-4d6a-9c4d-654c9ccc0137","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"I believe we are having our seasonal middle of the cycle drop right now. ","parentId":"3460b27f-fd17-4a58-877c-276fe2aa21c3","previousState":null},{"id":"3460b27f-fd17-4a58-877c-276fe2aa21c3","createdAt":"2023-04-27T20:18:21.610Z","value":74.37,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"6f488fb4-a4cf-4d6a-9c4d-654c9ccc0137","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"Nothing new; I believe this number plateaued into a new standard.","parentId":"1a1dfaeb-9fd8-458b-857a-3d5c63713174","previousState":null},{"id":"1a1dfaeb-9fd8-458b-857a-3d5c63713174","createdAt":"2023-04-17T15:13:18.010Z","value":74.06,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"6f488fb4-a4cf-4d6a-9c4d-654c9ccc0137","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"We reached a new plateau for this metric. \n\n","parentId":"84a3bc9f-2a6b-4d84-a87e-df47d4f777c5","previousState":null},{"id":"84a3bc9f-2a6b-4d84-a87e-df47d4f777c5","createdAt":"2023-03-31T13:35:02.295Z","value":74.73,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"6f488fb4-a4cf-4d6a-9c4d-654c9ccc0137","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"Nothing new. I think the last check-in explanation holds. ","parentId":"4ae2d663-5651-42cd-8369-03897820e734","previousState":null},{"id":"4ae2d663-5651-42cd-8369-03897820e734","createdAt":"2023-03-19T16:58:01.632Z","value":71,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"6f488fb4-a4cf-4d6a-9c4d-654c9ccc0137","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"MAU reached 71%, growing steadily during the last two weeks. We explain this phenomenon in the document (https://www.notion.so/Why-MAU-and-WAU-suddenly-rose-this-week-bc912330fff94f9496f7aa1625ed3e62).","parentId":"765d4d7c-8be7-4e8b-ad54-c86395d1a107","previousState":null},{"id":"765d4d7c-8be7-4e8b-ad54-c86395d1a107","createdAt":"2023-02-23T17:00:37.238Z","value":50,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"6f488fb4-a4cf-4d6a-9c4d-654c9ccc0137","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"This value has steadily increased in the past few weeks, probably because more companies are in the execution phase. \n\nhttps://metabase.getbud.co/dashboard/28?user_type=OKR%20owner","parentId":"62fb99c5-aa90-4324-ad19-225366809546","previousState":null},{"id":"62fb99c5-aa90-4324-ad19-225366809546","createdAt":"2023-02-07T21:59:01.954Z","value":43,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"6f488fb4-a4cf-4d6a-9c4d-654c9ccc0137","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"MAU started to grow. Igor and I noticed this indicator is affected by the churned clients. Since they compose the denominator of the metric (active users/total number of users). Notice that the active users will plummet first during the churning process, while the total number of users will fall after. Therefore, it will be normal that this metric will decrease in every month.","parentId":"861d3e57-6e13-48dd-a216-324c07178af6","previousState":null},{"id":"861d3e57-6e13-48dd-a216-324c07178af6","createdAt":"2023-01-30T18:14:49.505Z","value":28,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"6f488fb4-a4cf-4d6a-9c4d-654c9ccc0137","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"O MAU caiu muito nas últimas semanas. Ainda vale dizer que esse número está baixo devido ao início do ano. Como contamos os últimos 30 dias para o cômputo desta métrica, ainda temos o impacto do recesso da virada.","parentId":null,"previousState":null}],"objective":{"id":"df4804e3-d3a2-4027-818e-2c751248ffa3","createdAt":"2023-01-13T14:17:45.292Z","title":"Guide the users' routine amidst the chaos of strategy execution","description":null,"updatedAt":"2023-01-13T14:17:49.402Z","cycleId":"4f01f61e-1616-40fa-8363-a930a2db2351","ownerId":"5aec0149-5535-42fb-b3d3-c20a5