be6a","previousState":null},{"id":"424d450b-6074-439e-8dea-fc9a6200be6a","createdAt":"2023-06-11T19:43:47.721Z","value":24.8,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"79451465-50e3-4645-a707-276c2d525790","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"The number has grown probably because more companies are in execution phase. ","parentId":"2048fccc-1c59-4066-a8fe-15e8a23e2614","previousState":null},{"id":"2048fccc-1c59-4066-a8fe-15e8a23e2614","createdAt":"2023-05-15T13:20:13.707Z","value":20.3,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"79451465-50e3-4645-a707-276c2d525790","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"20.3 is the value for the middle of the month; I believe this number will increase a little more.\n\nWe are not focusing on the reach of our previous features. Currently, we are prioritizing new features.","parentId":"57842494-2903-47ca-a7f1-f5db7ff8c17c","previousState":null},{"id":"57842494-2903-47ca-a7f1-f5db7ff8c17c","createdAt":"2023-04-27T20:17:15.312Z","value":19.5,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"79451465-50e3-4645-a707-276c2d525790","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"This number is low; I must investigate why users dropped the feature. ","parentId":"24d7baa8-fcc5-49f2-b551-7dfe9af3696f","previousState":null},{"id":"24d7baa8-fcc5-49f2-b551-7dfe9af3696f","createdAt":"2023-04-17T15:11:59.486Z","value":36.1,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"79451465-50e3-4645-a707-276c2d525790","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"I think this metric will not have huge changes until we deliver the spotlight feature. ","parentId":"4081874f-f10f-48d8-a7b4-fa554cc75f66","previousState":null},{"id":"4081874f-f10f-48d8-a7b4-fa554cc75f66","createdAt":"2023-04-02T22:57:24.677Z","value":36.1,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"79451465-50e3-4645-a707-276c2d525790","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"The TeamView feature has reached 36.1% of active leaders during March.\n\nhttps://analytics.amplitude.com/bud/cha