":null}],"objective":{"id":"df4804e3-d3a2-4027-818e-2c751248ffa3","createdAt":"2023-01-13T14:17:45.292Z","title":"Guide the users' routine amidst the chaos of strategy execution","description":null,"updatedAt":"2023-01-13T14:17:49.402Z","cycleId":"4f01f61e-1616-40fa-8363-a930a2db2351","ownerId":"5aec0149-5535-42fb-b3d3-c20a5bda80c8","teamId":"f6790108-2b16-4077-bed0-103fc38175dd","mode":"PUBLISHED","cycle":{"id":"4f01f61e-1616-40fa-8363-a930a2db2351","createdAt":"2023-01-12T18:32:30.038Z","period":"2023","cadence":"YEARLY","active":true,"dateStart":"2023-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","dateEnd":"2023-12-31T00:00:00.000Z","updatedAt":"2023-01-12T18:32:30.038Z","teamId":"f6790108-2b16-4077-bed0-103fc38175dd","parentId":null}},"team":{"id":"f6790108-2b16-4077-bed0-103fc38175dd","createdAt":"2021-03-01T12:59:54.029Z","name":"Bud","updatedAt":"2021-10-12T16:39:15.305Z","ownerId":"16e46da6-39fc-4034-84c9-7b59a825d6e4","description":"Bud é a plataforma que te ajuda a implementar OKR de um jeito leve, envolvente e colaborativo.","gender":"MALE","parentId":null}},{"id":"1010607d-ac9f-47e6-8970-b8563d41dbde","createdAt":"2023-01-13T14:18:12.079Z","title":"Increase user NPS from 21 to 60","initialValue":"21","goal":"60","format":"NUMBER","type":"ASCENDING","updatedAt":"2023-02-07T21:41:34.703Z","ownerId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","objectiveId":"df4804e3-d3a2-4027-818e-2c751248ffa3","teamId":"f6790108-2b16-4077-bed0-103fc38175dd","description":"This metric comes from Typeform, sent by e-mail, and Hotjar within the application. \n\nNPS is used to measure customer satisfaction with our product. We had a decrease between Q3 and Q42022. Here, we aim to reach the previous values.\n\n","mode":"PUBLISHED","lastUpdatedBy":null,"commentCount":{"issue":0,"comment":0,"praisal":0,"question":0,"alignment":0,"suggestion":0,"improvement":0},"checkIns":[{"id":"ee2aff6f-0b0c-4769-9f7d-fb74a5ab9de3","createdAt":"2023-06-26T19:35:14.193Z","value":9,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"1010607d-ac9f-47e6-8970-b8563d41dbde","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"We started collecting this metric in the last week. Let's see how it goes in the next check-in. ","parentId":"fc0a6975-6ed2-4daa-abf2-a4fabf222ed1","previousState":null},{"id":"fc0a6975-6ed2-4daa-abf2-a4fabf222ed1","createdAt":"2023-06-11T19:42:16.091Z","value":9,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"1010607d-ac9f-47e6-8970-b8563d41dbde","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"I am confident this one will improve due to our efforts in reducing slowness in the platform. ","parentId":"a7854e71-5e2f-43b7-bc91-229dbf88d6b1","previousState":null},{"id":"a7854e71-5e2f-43b7-bc91-229dbf88d6b1","createdAt":"2023-05-15T13:16:53.710Z","value":9,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"1010607d-ac9f-47e6-8970-b8563d41dbde","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"We did not collect NPS and will wait until we have some performance improvements. \n\nDanilo did some great observability (mostly logging) to deeper understand our slowdown issues. ","parentId":"e8fff822-5d32-4c95-a0bd-3db9d22ff003","previousState":null},{"id":"e8fff822-5d32-4c95-a0bd-3db9d22ff003","createdAt":"2023-04-27T20:15:21.312Z","value":9,"confidence":100,"keyResultId":"1010607d-ac9f-47e6-8970-b8563d41dbde","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"Although this number dropped, I think we have triggered plans for action to raise NPS through performance improvements. ","parentId":"d9008030-7a40-4ae5-889a-b7941adb8395","previousState":null},{"id":"d9008030-7a40-4ae5-889a-b7941adb8395","createdAt":"2023-04-17T15:10:38.409Z","value":4,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"1010607d-ac9f-47e6-8970-b8563d41dbde","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"We had a huge drop in NPS due to some slowdown issues in the platform. We have analysis and improvement plans on the way for this matter.","parentId":"e36109c9-e1fd-4580-8a6e-494648419c98","previousState":null},{"id":"e36109c9-e1fd-4580-8a6e-494648419c98","createdAt":"2023-04-02T22:54:18.340Z","value":61,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"1010607d-ac9f-47e6-8970-b8563d41dbde","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"We did not finish the collection because we reached Hotjar's limit of responses.","parentId":"05bfbbee-6f79-44e8-b7e9-5e173e78cad2","previousState":null},{"id":"05bfbbee-6f79-44e8-b7e9-5e173e78cad2","createdAt":"2023-03-19T16:52:51.162Z","value":61,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"1010607d-ac9f-47e6-8970-b8563d41dbde","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"We did not have any updates since the last measurement. But my hopes are not high for this one since we got some instability in the platform during the last month.","parentId":"45f73d7d-69ce-4cae-bd4e-305654f7e1fc","previousState":null},{"id":"45f73d7d-69ce-4cae-bd4e-305654f7e1fc","createdAt":"2023-02-23T17:28:34.603Z","value":61,"confidence":66,"keyResultId":"1010607d-ac9f-47e6-8970-b8563d41dbde","userId":"94c1238b-182d-4861-a304-dac9f35e2391","comment":"https://insights.hotjar.com/sites/2216269/surveys/results/778913?date=last-30-days\n\nWe have been measuring the results since 14 Feb (sample size = 13), and we are not certain about why the value has increased. But we have been working on evolving the platform's performance in this quarter.","parentId":"668818d3-84d3-4f5e-983b-1305a7f74e24","previousState":null},{"id":"668818d3-84d3-4f5e-983b-1305a7f74e24","createdAt":"2query: SELECT "KeyResult"."id" AS "KeyResult_id", "KeyResult"."created_at" AS "KeyResult_created_at", "KeyResult"."title" AS "KeyResult_title", "KeyResult"."initial_value" AS "KeyResult_initial_value", "KeyResult"."goal" AS "KeyResult_goal", "KeyResult"."format" AS "KeyResult_format", "KeyResult"."type" AS "KeyResult_type", "KeyResult"."updated_at" AS "KeyResult_updated_at", "KeyResult"."owner_id" AS "KeyResult_owner_id", "KeyResult"."objective_id" AS "KeyResult_objective_id", "KeyResult"."team_id" AS "KeyResult_team_id", "KeyResult"."d